128	\subsection{The short exact sequence of sheaves}
129	
130	The connecting homomorphism of the Mayer--Vietoris sequence is built from a short exact sequence of sheaves of $k$-modules obtained by sheafifying the Yoneda embedding composed with the free-$k$-module functor.
